OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775999464
OL,3,CDriver rescued after lorry overturns
OL,4,Con Oxfordshire roundabout
OL,6,FA lorry driver has been rescued from
OL,7,Fhis cab after his vehicle overturned
OL,8,Fon a busy roundabout near Bicester.
OL,10,FCrews were called to Baynard's Green
OL,11,Froundabout at the junction of the A43
OL,12,Fand B4100 just after 5.15pm on
OL,13,FSaturday.
OL,15,FThe driver sustained minor injuries
OL,16,Fand was unable to get out of the lorry.
OL,18,FCrews from Bicester, Banbury, and
OL,19,FKidlington helped with the rescue
OL,20,Foperation, which closed the road for
OL,21,Feveral hours.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
