OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775999464
OL,3,CDriver rescued after lorry overturns
OL,4,Con Oxfordshire roundabout
OL,6,FThames Valley Police and South Central
OL,7,FAmbulance Service were also in
OL,8,Fattendance, and a local recovery firm
OL,9,Fremoved the vehicle.
OL,11,F"This incident was a fantastic example
OL,12,Fof our blue light partners working
OL,13,Ftogether to achieve a successful
OL,14,Foutcome," the fire service said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
