OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775999464
OL,3,CDriver rescued after lorry overturns
OL,4,Con Oxfordshire roundabout
OL,6,FThe driver suffering from minor
OL,7,Finjuries was unable to leave the
OL,8,Fvehicle and was released by the fire
OL,9,Fservice after a handover from South
OL,10,FCentral Ambulance Service NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust who were in
OL,12,Fattendance.
OL,14,FA road closure was in place which has
OL,15,Fnow been reopened whilst Thames Valley
OL,16,FPolice dealt with the rest of the
OL,17,Fincident supported by a local recovery
OL,18,Ffirm to move the vehicle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
